entry.summary:
Vendor: STARMAXDESIGN
Type:
Price: 0.00

As a simulated building material, marble wall panels restore marble's surface texture and color through film technology, presenting a texture and aesthetic feeling similar to natural marble. Due to the thin film technology, the marble wall panels are lighter in weight and easier to handle and install than real marble materials.

This is an essential advantage for construction work and interior decoration, saving manpower and time costs. Additionally, marble wall panel is relatively easy to maintain and clean. Since the surface is made of anti-fouling film material, it can effectively prevent the infiltration of stains and keep the wall clean and smooth.
